Package: hsir
Type: Package
Title: High-Speed Image Recognition
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Jannik Vindeloev <jannik@example.com>
Maintainer: Jannik Vindeloev <jannik@example.com>
Description: Lightweight, fast and memory efficient image recognition utilities.
    Optimized for performance with efficient data structures and algorithms.
    Includes functions for reading and processing HSI (Hyperspectral Imaging) data
    in PAM format with optimized binary reading and thumbnail generation.
Depends: R (>= 3.6.0)
Imports: 
    data.table,
    matrixStats,
    fastmatrix,
    collapse
Suggests: 
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    knitr,
    rmarkdown,
    roxygen2 (>= 7.2.3),
    graphics
License: proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 7.2.3
